data.description: Immaculate, 3-Bed, 2-Bath home in California City, displaying modern features & amenities. Stylish tile & wood-like flooring, classy fixtures, vast windows & a pristine design. Lovely, open floor plan w/ an impressive Kitchen, boasting granite counters, center island, stainless-steel appliances, designer cabinetry and a grand walk-in pantry. The formal dining room is conveniently situated nearby, great for entertaining while cooking. The Living room is warm & inviting w/ bright windows & a seating alcove. The family room is an added bonus w/ its built-in shelving and tri-sided, exquisite fireplace allowing for relaxation and socialization. Master bedroom has its own private powder room w/ dual sinks, shower and a separate deep & wide jetted bath tub. The huge walk-in closet is a total plus!!. All bedrooms have plenty of space for work & play, sleep & storage. Special touches throughout & of course, all are creatively & neatly designed. The front & back yards will sell you for sure w/ the oversized lot, well thought-out landscaping, covered patio, RV parking and so much more. Prime location, near shopping centers, freeway and more. This house is perfect for those serving in the military, larger families, or basically anyone that is looking to live in a comfortable & friendly neighborhood. Take a peak, fall-in-love & make it yours! Hurry...because with its amazing condition and great price tag, this one will not stay on the market for long!!
